com.amplifyframework.core.plugin

Interface Plugin

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AnalyticsCategoryPlugin, AuthPlugin, CategoryPlugin, StoragePlugin

    public interface Plugin
    Interface that defines the contract that every plugin in Amplify System will adhere to.
